  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in the ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Stir in ground cumin, smoked paprika, and cayenne pepper.",
    "Add hominy, chicken broth, and shredded chicken, bringing to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in mayonnaise, nuka-pickle, and lime juice.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped cilantro.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
